videos.headline: Ohio WR makes impressive catch
videos.description: Bobcats' QB Nathan Rourke throws a pass to WR Andrew Meyer who makes a leaping catch for 24-yards.

videos.headline: Ohio QB breaks tackle for TD
videos.description: Bobcats' QB Nathan Rourke takes the snap, then breaks a tackle to score the touchdown.

videos.headline: Bobcats' getting fancy with a trick play
videos.description: K Michael Farkas fakes the FG and throws the pass to LS Jake Hale for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Ohios' offense extends their lead
videos.description: Bobcats' QB Nathan Rourke throws a pass to Troy Mangen for a 10-yard TD.

videos.headline: Kansas' RB rips off huge run for TD
videos.description: Khalil Herbert takes the handoff and goes 56-yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Kansas cuts the lead right before half
videos.description: QB Payton Bender completes the pass to WR Chase Harrell who makes a great catch for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Kansas' D makes a huge play  in the redzone
videos.description: CB Mike Lee makes a crucial interception to prevent a touchdown.

videos.headline: Ohio capitalizing off Kansas' mistakes
videos.description: RB A.J. Ouellette scores an  easy 8-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ohio defense coming up big
videos.description: The Bobcats' send a blitz and Dylan Conner sacks Payton Bender for a 3rd down stop.
